s in Vietnam]]\n[[Category:B\u1eafc Giang| ]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n<!-- See Template:Infobox settlement for additional fields and descriptions -->\n<!-- Basic info  ---------------->| name                            = B\u1eafc Giang\n| official_name                   = B\u1eafc Giang City\n| other_name                      = \n| native_name                     = Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 B\u1eafc Giang\n| nickname                        = \n| settlement_type                 = [[Provincial city (Vietnam)|City (Class-2)]]<!-- e.g. Town, Village, City, etc.-->\n| total_type                      = <!-- to set a non-standard label for total area and population rows -->\n| motto                           = <!-- images and maps  ----------->\n| image_skyline                   = BacGiang City.JPG\n| imagesize                       = 250px\n| image_caption                   = \n| image_flag                      = \n| flag_size                       = \n| image_seal                      = Emblem of Bacgiang City.png\n| seal_size                       = \n| image_shield                    = \n| shield_size                     = \n| image_blank_emblem              = \n| blank_emblem_type               = \n| blank_emblem_size               = \n| image_map                       = \n| mapsize                         = \n| map_caption                     = \n| image_map1                      = \n| mapsize1                        = \n| map_caption1                    = \n| image_dot_map                   = \n| dot_mapsize                     = \n| dot_map_caption                 = \n| dot_x                           = \n| dot_y                           = \n| pushpin_map                     = Vietnam <!-- the name of a location map as per http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Template:Location_map -->\n| pushpin_label_position          = <!-- the position of the pushpin label: left, right, top, bottom, none -->\n| pushpin_map_caption             = Location of in Vietnam\n| pushpi